queries.sql: SELECT `m`.*, `mk`.`kecamatan` as `nama_kec`, `md`.`desa` as `nama_desa`, `mkab`.`kab` as `nama_kab`, `p`.`posisi`, `mjk`.`jenis_kelamin` as `jk` FROM `mitra` `m` LEFT JOIN `master`.`master_kec` `mk` ON `mk`.`id` = CONCAT(81, m.kab, m.kec) LEFT JOIN `master`.`master_desa` `md` ON `md`.`id` = CONCAT(81, m.kab, m.kec, m.desa) LEFT JOIN `master`.`master_kab` `mkab` ON `mkab`.`id` = `m`.`kab` LEFT JOIN `posisi` `p` ON `p`.`id` = `m`.`posisi` LEFT JOIN `master_jk` `mjk` ON `mjk`.`id` = `m`.`jk`
